# Ramen Jiro-style Website - Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Create a one-page branding website for a "Jiro-style" (G-kei) ramen shop.
The site needs to convey **"Impact," "Volume," and "Addiction."**
Design should be bold, aggressive, and appetizing.

## User Review Required
- **Design Vibe**: Classic "Yellow Background + Black Text + Red Accents" (The standard Jiro look).
- **Content**: Focus on the "Call" (Topping order system) and the visual impact of the ramen.

